1
00:00:03,883 --> 00:00:06,691
In urban areas, faecal sludge
often looks like this.

2
00:00:06,891 --> 00:00:09,963
It is extremely liquid and contains
few solids.

3
00:00:10,547 --> 00:00:14,338
Often, more than 95%
of faecal sludge is water.

4
00:00:14,538 --> 00:00:16,541
Dewatering of this sludge usually
requires a lot of space

5
00:00:16,741 --> 00:00:18,634
that is commonly not available
in urban areas.

6
00:00:19,266 --> 00:00:21,976
In this module we introduce you
to settling-thickening tanks

7
00:00:22,176 --> 00:00:25,263
that can reduce the volume that
requires dewatering by more than 50%.

8
00:00:25,854 --> 00:00:28,485
No, it's not by magic.
It is by gravity.

9
00:00:29,687 --> 00:00:31,941
Following this module, you will
be able to explain

10
00:00:32,141 --> 00:00:34,646
the treatment process and operation
of settling-thickening tanks.

11
00:00:34,846 --> 00:00:37,315
Discuss operation and maintenance
requirements,

12
00:00:37,515 --> 00:00:40,559
and name design parameters specific
to settling-thickening tanks.

13
