00:04:33,623 --> 00:04:36,538
The settling velocity and the solid
liquid separation effeciency

87
00:04:36,738 --> 00:04:39,903
are design parameters that are
specific to settling-thickening tanks.

88
00:04:40,103 --> 00:04:44,043
The settling velocity is an estimate
of the speed with which

89
00:04:44,244 --> 00:04:47,300
solids settle to the bottom
of a settling-thickening tank.

90
00:04:47,564 --> 00:04:49,412
If the speed with which the solids
travel through 

91
00:04:49,612 --> 00:04:53,462
the settling-thickening tank
is faster than the settling velocity

92
00:04:53,662 --> 00:04:56,662
the sludge will leave the tank
with the effluent.

93
