00:05:00,717 --> 00:05:03,599
If the settling velocity is faster
than the velocity with which

95
00:05:03,799 --> 00:05:07,848
the solids travel through the tank,
the solids will settle out at the bottom.

96
00:05:08,681 --> 00:05:11,477
Based on experience from Accra, 
Kampala, and Dakar,

97
00:05:11,677 --> 00:05:16,257
